Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好 好 好\NOkay, okay, okay, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.09,0:01:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的\NOkay...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.79,0:02:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,对 对\NYes... Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.90,0:02:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,对 对 快点 快点 没错 没错\NYes, yes, come on... Come on, yes! Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.73,0:02:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,到了 到了 到了\NOkay. Okay. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了 找到了\NHere we go, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.28,0:02:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好 好 该死\NOkay. Okay. Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.28,0:02:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,能用 能用 一定得能用\NWork. Work. Work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,标准组... 好...\NStandard... Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.48,0:03:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,标准组 你们...你们能收到吗？\NStandard, can you- can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我是纳伦\NThis is Naren.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我 呃...\NAnd I've, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟其他人走散了\NI've been separated, uh, from the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.86,0:03:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该没事\NAnd I think I'm okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道我现在到底在哪儿\Nbut I'm not sure where I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.70,0:03:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没走到过那么深 所以我也...\NI've never been out this far before, so I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才有个...\NThere was this, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我没看清 可是 呃...\NI didn't get a good look at it, but there was, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.04,0:03:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这里还有别的东西\Nthere's something else in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.41,0:03:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你们快来\NI need you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,明白吗？快来接我 求你们了\NOkay? I need you guys to get me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,该死 快来把我弄出去\NFuck, I need you guys to come out and get me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.88,0:03:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,麻烦来接我 求你们了 标准组\NCan you... can you come, please, standard?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,收到了吗？\NStandard?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,完了\NOh, fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.73,0:03:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,完了\NFuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.60,0:03:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,该死 该死\NFuck! Fuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,该死 搞什么鬼？\NOh, shit... What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[钱不够 没...]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.18,0:05:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？\NWhat the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,完了 完了 完了\NFuck! Fuck! Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.38,0:06:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,完了\NFuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 完了 完了\NFuck, fuck, fuck! Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[后室]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[山脊公寓]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,人人都有自己的老路 固有的习惯...\NWe all have our loops, our habits...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,总是原地打转...\N...behaviors that keep us walking in circles...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:08:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,一遍遍用同样的办法\N...reaching for the same solutions over and over again,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[克船长的家具百宝库]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.62,0:08:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,却指望能走出新路\Nthinking each time they'll take you somewhere new.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但没用\NBut they don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,因为大脑\NAnd still,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.44,0:08:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,总是习惯于 走阻力最小的路径\Nit's the neural pathway of least resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[无良商家]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你建立了心理防线\NA path you made.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.34,0:08:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,小时候 这套防线保护了你\NIt's the one that kept you safe when you were a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.42,0:08:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[大促销 大降价]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你养成了疏远别人\NYou learned to push people away
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.09,0:08:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,避免伤害的本能反应\Nbefore they could hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,现在\NAnd now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.13,0:08:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}[逾期账单]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.26,0:08:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你都成年了\Nas an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.93,0:08:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,却还是走不出来\Nyou're still stuck right where you started.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,把自己关里面\NAlone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:09:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我有人陪啊\NI mean, I'm not lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我有店员 还有顾客\NI have employees and... customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.82,0:09:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我没说有人陪 我说的是你把自己关在里面\NI didn't say lonely. I said alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 是 但是...\NYeah, well, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.29,0:09:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我老是伤人\NI hurt people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不想 可我就这德行\NI don't want to. It's just the way I'm wired.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,可能就该把自己关起来\NSo maybe I deserve to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.23,0:09:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,谁活该把自己关着吗？\NDo you think anyone deserves to be alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我说不好 但怎么说呢\NI don't know, but, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,也许这样也挺好\Nmaybe it's not such a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,自我封闭...\NBeing alone feels...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.34,0:09:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,已经刻进骨子里了\Ndeeply ingrained.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我理解\NI understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你有梦想 但老是受挫\NYou've had dreams and a lot of resistance,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,身边也没人支持你\Nnot a lot of support in realizing those dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.92,0:09:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,当伤害变成了...\NAnd when we've experienced...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,一次次家常便饭\Nhurt again and again,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.69,0:09:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就会习惯性地想\Nwe start to expect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.26,0:09:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,“哦 这路我熟”\NIt's like, "Oh, I know this path.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.63,0:09:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,“下场一定是一样的”\NI know where it goes."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,所以...\NSo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.83,0:09:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你想不想摆脱这个死循环\Nare you interested in forging a new path
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,走出一条不同的路？\Nand see where that leads?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊 我来都来了 就试试吧\NSure. Why not? You know, I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\NGreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.61,0:10:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,要不咱们重温一下\NSo I want to revisit
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.11,0:10:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,之前练过的那个\Nan exercise we've done before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.61,0:10:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,角色扮演\NThe role play.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.01,0:10:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哦 演戏那套？ - 对\N- Oh, the acting thing? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.85,0:10:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我觉得太丢人了 - 我懂\N- I feel stupid doing that. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.82,0:10:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但既然还有点时间 就....\NBut we have a few minutes. Let's, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,试一下吧 稍微试试\NYeah, let's try. A little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.19,0:10:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们先定个场景\NLet's set the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,回到芭芭拉离开你的那晚\NLet's go back to the night that Barbara left you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.03,0:10:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说她把我从我家给撵出去的那晚？\NYou mean the night she kicked me out of my own house?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,对\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我演我自己\NI'm playing myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我演芭芭拉 - 别忘了 那可是我的房子\N- And I'll be Barbara. - It is my house, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,房贷都是我在还\NI'm the one paying for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我知道 - 好吧\N- I know. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好 那...\NOkay, so, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那天我回家晚了 具体几点我忘了\NI got home late. I don't know how late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候她已经睡了 应该是半夜了\NUh... She was already asleep. Maybe midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.26,0:10:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,她一般睡得早...算了 这不重要\NShe usually goes to bed before... It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.16,0:10:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,重点是我当时在厨房\NThe point is, I was in the kitchen, and, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,有个杯子 我把杯子打碎了\Nthe glass, I broke the glass,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,她听见动静跑下来 然后...\Nand she comes running down to see what happened, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.50,0:11:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就闹起来了\Nthings escalated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那你当时什么感受？\NAnd how do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时...\NWell, I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时喝多了...\NI was drunk, and, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.85,0:11:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我觉得自己挺蠢的 你懂吧\NI-I felt stupid, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我就火了 因为 因为我把杯子打碎了\NI was angry, because... because I broke the glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.85,0:11:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你能对着我再说一遍吗？\NCan you say that to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.62,0:11:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对着你 对着芭芭拉？ - 对\N- Uh, what, to-to Barbara? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,额...对不起 把你吵醒了\NUm... I'm sorry that I woke you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.20,0:11:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你能早点回家\NMaybe if you'd come home earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们今晚本该待在一起的\Nwe could have spent the evening together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我在加班 你懂的\NNo, I was... I was working, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,下班后我就直接回来了\NI came straight home after work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,诚实点吧\NBe honest with me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你身上那酒气我都闻得见\NI can smell it on your breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.88,0:11:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我就喝了点啤酒\NI had a few beers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.55,0:11:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,一点是多少？\NDefine a few.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.18,0:11:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,唉 今天太累了\NWell, it was a hard day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.62,0:11:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我得喝点放松放松\NI needed to wind down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.05,0:11:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你不成天在放松吗\NAll you ever do is wind down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:11:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,成天呆在那店里\NYou're always at the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要孩子 对吧？\NYou want kids, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.26,0:12:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 咱们都想要 - 但你要知道...\N- We both do. - Well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,养家得花钱\Nhaving a family takes money,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,总得有人去挣钱\Nwhich means someone has to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,除非现在当学生\NUnless being a professional student
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,也能算份工作了\Nis considered a job these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.34,0:12:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能这么说 你知道我得休学一段时间\NThat's not fair. You know I had to take time off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己跟不上 凭什么怪我\NWell, it's not my fault if you can't keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,连法学院都搞不定\NHow are you going to be a lawyer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.41,0:12:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,还想怎么当律师？\Nif you can't even handle law school?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.78,0:12:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,当你这个三十岁的大一新生\NWho do you think pays for everything
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.35,0:12:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,在学校里到处瞎逛时\Nwhile you're gallivanting around campus
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,也不想想谁在供你上学？\Nlike a 30-year-old freshman?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.65,0:12:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你个提示 就是我\NI'll give you a hint: it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你上学是我供 休学是我供\NI pay for your school, I pay for your time off school,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,房子还是我供\NI pay for the roof over your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.86,0:12:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我能说句话吗？ - 不 没门 \N- Can I talk now? - No! No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你真混到毕业了\NBecause I'd like to know, what do you think happens
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒想知道结果会怎样？\Nif you do manage to graduate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,生个娃账单继续甩给我？\NYou know, you pop out a kid, then leave me with the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.47,0:12:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,还是你终于成大忙人了\NOr am I stuck at home changing diapers because
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我就得天天在家给娃换屎尿？\Nyou're too busy working for the first time in your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你这话太狠了 - 我是在说实话\N- Now you're being cruel. - I'm being honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.38,0:12:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为这就是你的追求\NI thought that's what you always wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.61,0:12:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你没考上建筑师 并不代表...\NJust because you didn't get to be an architect doesn't mean--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,老子就是建筑师！\NI am a fucking architect!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.68,0:13:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我成天得在那破店里卖这些玩意儿\NGod damn it, I'm just stuck selling shit furniture because
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就因为某个懒猪在家混吃等死 根本不肯出力\Nsomeone won't get off their fat fucking ass and help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克 现在感觉怎么样？\NHow do you feel, Clark?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我在跟谁说话呢？\NWho am I talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是我 在你面前  - 哦 你啊 好吧\N- Me, here, now. - You? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.68,0:13:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那个...\NUm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.44,0:13:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 我不是故意那样说...\NI'm sorry, I didn't mean to, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,就是 刚才发火了\N...you know, get angry
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,情绪失控了那种\Nor lose my temper or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.82,0:13:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,练习的目的就在这儿\NThat's the purpose of the whole exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.12,0:13:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个不错的开始\NThis is a good start.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.02,0:13:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,正视你的感受\NTo feel what you feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,然后找出一条新路\Nand then learn to identify a new path.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你的反应其实很正常\NYour reaction was actually quite normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,呵呵 我就这德行\NWell, that's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.44,0:13:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,喂！伙计们！\NWell, ahoy there, mateys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:14:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,还打算把金币全砸在那些冤大头家具上？ \NTired of spending your hard-earned doubloons on overpriced furniture?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,想买惊掉下巴的跳海价吗？\NLooking for deals that'll shiver your timbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快来克船长的家具百宝库！\NThen come on down to Cap'n Clark's Ottoman Empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,圣克拉拉谷的头号家具大卖场\Nthe Santa Clara Valley's favorite warehouse and showrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,卧室 客厅 餐厅 书房 浴室\NYou'll find bedrooms, living rooms,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.36,0:14:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,全屋家具 应有尽有！\Ndinettes, dens and bathrooms aplenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.36,0:14:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,刚买房的？来这儿就对了！[拆分]\NFirst-time homeowners? We've got ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,新当爹妈的？\NNew parents looking for Billy's first crib?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,来这就对了！\NWe've got ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.43,0:14:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,时髦现代样样全\NFrom the latest in modern design
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.37,0:14:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,经典复古通通有\Nto the classic styles of yesteryear,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.71,0:14:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,价格低到没对手\Nit's all here and it's all a steal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦 波莉？\NWhat's that, Polly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.81,0:14:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,信用卡里钱不够？\NYou're worried about credit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈！在克船长这儿 钱不够 没问题！\NHa! Cap'n Clark says no credit, no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,快来潜入顶级家具海洋\NSail the high seas of high quality,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.95,0:14:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,把钱的问题统统抛在脑后\Nand leave your money problems at the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.89,0:14:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,今天就来店里\NWalk in today
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,把梦想直接搬回家！\Nand get your dream sectional lounger,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,桌椅板凳 灯具摆件随便挑！\Nkitchen table, floor lamp, and bed frame here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.56,0:14:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,克船长的家具百宝库\Nat Cap'n Clark's Ottoman Empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,就在680号公路 凯皮托与麦基路口\Nlocated at Capitol and McKee, just off the 680.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿吼！赶紧过来...\NArr! Walk in today...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:14:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,翘起二郎腿\N...kick your feet back,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.14,0:15:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,当你的家具大王！\Nand enjoy an empire of your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.37,0:15:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟 国王得有王座\NFor every sultan deserves a throne,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,而你的专属王座 就在这儿等着你\Nand we've got one with your name on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.64,0:15:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就在克船长的...\Nhere at Cap'n Clark's--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,卧槽\NNo way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 克拉克 没事吧？ - 快把相机关了\N- Clark, you good? - Turn the camera off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.02,0:15:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不不 拍得好 这种花絮才有趣\NNo, no, it's good. It's outtake stuff, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 赶紧给老子关掉 - 好吧...我的天\N- Turn the fucking camera off. - Okay... Jesus...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.76,0:15:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 要帮忙吗？\NYou, uh, you need help?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.26,0:15:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不用 我自己来\NNo, I got it, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.89,0:15:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那个...\NUm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还要重拍吗？ - 不拍了\N- Are we going again, or...? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.56,0:15:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,小凯 去开门开业吧\NKat, you can open the store now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,早就开了\NWe've been open.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[大促销 大降价]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,0:15:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计 我还是没搞懂\NYou know, dude, I still don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你演的是海盗还是国王？\NAre you, like, a pirate or a sultan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 最好还是明确一下 - 我是个...闭嘴\N- Just be good to establish it. - I'm a... Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,刨花板做的破椅子\NPiece of cheap particleboard bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,快把这东西弄走 听到没？\NClear this stuff up, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,给你\NHere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.62,0:15:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[大促销 大降价]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.07,0:16:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\NSorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样 查出来没？\NHow's it looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,电表没问题\NMeter reads fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.27,0:16:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,电费要是高 只能是你自己用得多\NIf your bill's coming in high, that's on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那跳电的事怎么说 打烊后就出现\NWhat about the outages? That happens after hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,没准是荧光灯出问题 导致跳闸了\NDon't know. Fluorescents must be tripping a breaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,一打烊我就把顶灯都关了\NI turn the overheads off when the store closes,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,还没闪之前就关了\Nbefore the power gets weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.59,0:16:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 这样电费不该少点吗？\NAnyway, wouldn't that just make the bills go down?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,配电箱在哪儿？\NWhere's your breaker box?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.23,0:16:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我不是专家\NI'm no expert,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但我之前看过了 没看出什么问题\Nbut I checked earlier, and everything looks okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.90,0:16:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你说灯会闪 - 对 整个店都闪\N- You said the lights flicker. - Yeah, the whole store does.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是吗？ - 只是不一起闪\N- Huh. - Just not at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.74,0:16:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,有一晚是楼上\NOne night, I lose the power upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,下一晚就变成了楼下 完全没规律\NNext night, it's down here. There's no rhyme or...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.22,0:16:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,谁装的这鬼东西？\NWho the hell installed this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:16:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这房子买来就布好线了\NWell, the building came wired.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.46,0:16:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然有点年头 但也不至于不能用\NI mean, it's dated, but it's not that old.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.10,0:17:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你来看看这个\NTake a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,之前没这东西\NThat wasn't there before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.94,0:17:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,也许是我没注意到 我不是专家\NOr... maybe I didn't notice. Like I say, I'm no expert.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.34,0:17:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么是斜着的？\NWhy-why is it... why is it going that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.34,0:17:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,应该问问\NBetter question:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这东西到底接到哪儿了\Nwhat is it even connected to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.92,0:17:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,懂吗？\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,小凯 楼上灯怎么样？\NKat! How's the power?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.86,0:17:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛？\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,上面有反应吗？\NAnything happen up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼\NWhat the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.53,0:17:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,老鼠回来了\NThe rat's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 灯还正常吧 - 正常\N- But the power's on. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.07,0:17:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为咱们把老鼠给干掉了\NI thought we killed the rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.74,0:17:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们才杀了一只\NWe killed  a  rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.78,0:17:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这就是问题原因吗？- 没道理啊\N- So is this the problem? - Don't see how.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.65,0:17:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,电路根本不走这里\NPower can't even go through this part of the circuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.58,0:17:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,它纯粹是...\NIt's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.78,0:17:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,摆设\Nthere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,被哪个笨蛋随便塞进去的\NLike some schmo just stuck it in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.26,0:18:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你是否觉得生活像被隔在了一层玻璃之后？\NDo you ever feel like you're living behind glass?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,看着世界在眼前上演\NWatching life happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.64,0:18:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,自己却只能旁观？\Nbut never really stepping into it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.84,0:18:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 是时候打开心灵之窗了\NMaybe it's time to open the window within.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.34,0:18:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以重新定义自己的人生\NYou can be the author of your own design
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.65,0:18:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们每个人 都值得拥有另一次机会\Nbecause we all deserve another chance
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.18,0:18:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,让梦想重新启航\Nto fulfill our dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你相信改变是可能的\NThe moment you believe change is possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你就已经开始了这段旅程\Nyou've already begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.21,0:18:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[《心灵之窗》]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.75,0:18:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,立即订购《心灵之窗》\NOrder The Window Within
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,以及配套的三辑音频课程\Nand the companion three-part audio program,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.69,0:18:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,《引导之门》 均由玛丽·克莱因医生倾力呈现\NGuided Openings, by Dr. Mary Klein.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,现价24.95美元 运费另计\NAvailable now for $24.95 plus shipping.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.53,0:18:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,请拨打1-800-555-0199\NCall 1-800-555-0199.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.74,0:18:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,开辟一条新路 永远不晚\NIt's never too late to forge a new path.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.71,0:19:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你居然还在信任纸质文件夹\NSo, you're still trusting paper folders,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,贴错标签的磁带 还有个谁拿把钥匙\Nmislabeled tapes, and a locked filing cabinet
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,就能开的文件柜？\Nthat anyone with a spare key can open?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,信息决定企业的生死\NYour business runs on information,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但大多数公司却把数据当成了堆杂物...\Nyet most companies treat their data like clutter...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.72,0:19:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那个信号不是小行星\NThat small blip is not an asteroid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是一艘飞船 它咬住我们了\NIt's a spaceship, and it's on our tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.03,0:19:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 它在靠近 - 不可能 里格娜\N- It's getting closer. - Impossible, Rigna.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.46,0:19:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不可能发现我们 雷达隐身还开着呢\NThey couldn't have spotted us. We have our radar shield on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.23,0:19:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 长官 但他们追上来了\NI know that, sir, but they are gaining on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.77,0:19:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,难道地球人有某种秘密设备\NIs it possible Earth has a secret device
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.71,0:19:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,能穿透我们的雷达隐身罩？\Nthat can penetrate our radar shield?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[（1970年圣克鲁斯现代主义建筑设计论坛）]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.04,0:20:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,垃圾\NPiece of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么 你要这样对待自己？\NWhy did you do this to yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.77,0:21:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎么来到这里的？\NHow did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.14,0:21:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你的意识 就像一个装满记忆的房间\NYour consciousness is a room full of memories
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,它在时刻重构 在无限演变\Nthat is constantly evolving.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.38,0:21:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,在现实生活中\NBut as you walk through life,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,未经训练的心灵会开始筑墙\Nthe untrained mind can start to build walls,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.95,0:21:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,建立屏障\Nput up barriers
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,隔绝外界\Nto protect itself from the outside world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.36,0:21:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这是本能反应\NIt's a natural response.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.66,0:21:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们常常对此毫无察觉\NSomething we are often unaware of.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.50,0:21:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但久而久之\NBut if gone unchecked,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.63,0:21:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你会发现 自己被囚禁了\Nit can leave you feeling trapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.37,0:21:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你会说服自己\NYou can become convinced that the world outside
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,外面的世界不需要你\Nis better off without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.54,0:21:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你会告诉自己 自己不配被爱\NThat you never deserve the relationships you've had.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.81,0:21:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,于是 你只能蜷缩在窗后\NResigned to watch your life unfold
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.21,0:21:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,当个旁观者 静静地看着生活上演\Nfrom behind a lone window.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.38,0:21:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但我能帮你\NI can help you open it now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.99,0:21:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,因为窗户 并没有锁上\Nbecause the window isn't locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.66,0:22:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,门闩 也可以被打开\NThe latch was never broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.23,0:22:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好跨过去了吗？\NAre you ready to step through?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.17,0:22:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,去夺回属于你的东西\NSo that you can reclaim that which was once yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.77,0:22:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,去重新主宰你的生命\Nand take back control of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.21,0:22:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,去过你想过的人生\NThe life you want to be living.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.08,0:22:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,卸下过去的沉重\NUnburdened by the traumas of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.75,0:22:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,走出那些你亲手打造的围墙\NFree of the confines you had built.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.12,0:22:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...所以我想...\N...to leave, and so I decided...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.19,0:22:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,开辟一条属于你自己的路\NAnd free to choose a path of your own design.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.96,0:23:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[店铺名称需要翻译]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.58,0:23:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[停车]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.13,0:23:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 牛仔们 快瞧这边！\NWell, hey there, cowboys and cowgirls!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.70,0:23:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,想在里奥格兰德河这块地盘\NAre you looking to rustle up the best deals
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.93,0:23:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,抢到最便宜的家具吗？\Nthis side of the Rio Grande?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.27,0:23:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,刺\NPrick.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.44,0:23:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,咿吼！快来大韦恩家具店！\NWell, yeehaw, I say yeehaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.44,0:23:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,买了我们的餐厅套装\NHere at Big Wayne's, our dining room sets
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.81,0:23:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,就跟挖到金矿一样！\Nare gonna make you feel like you just struck gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.31,0:23:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,别去管那些破店\NSo don't even think about going anyplace else.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.26,0:23:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}[大韦恩家具店]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.68,0:23:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,认准大韦恩 认准金色招...\NBig Wayne's, just look for the golden--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.10,0:23:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,垃圾\NWhat the...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.52,0:24:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,该死 看我怎么修理你\NStupid... Fuck! Piece of shit!